[SN]TITLE[SN]
3ft deep sink hole appears in road in Heath, Cardiff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A sink hole reported to be 3ft deep has appeared in a road in Cardiff.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police said the 0.9m hole on Talygarn Street, in the Heath area of the city, was reported at about 18:00 BST on Thursday.
Cardiff council's highways department is dealing with the problem, police added.
